            "text": "Tooth fairies pinch their victims' fingers, noses, ears, or similar protruding body parts. Each enemy in the swarm's space takes 2d6 bludgeoning damage (DC 20 basic Reflex save). Creatures that critically fail this save are sickened 1 from the pain.",
